  The "runverbatim" package provides a simple means of executing the
  contents of verbatim environments and including the results within
  a document.

  It exploits features of the "listings" and "fancyvrb" packages.

  Comments, suggestions and bug reports (with version number and the
  keyword "runverbatim" in the subject of the message) to <tim@tbrk.org>.

